long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Among Us extension provide you with Among Us on PC new tab page. Created for Among Us fans.

Among Us is a 2018 online multiplayer social deduction game developed and published by American game studio Innersloth. It was released on iOS and Android devices in June 2018 and on Windows in November 2018, featuring cross-platform play between these platforms. The game was also ported for the Nintendo Switch in December 2020, and has planned releases for the Xbox One, Xbox Series X and Series S, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation 5 in 2021.

Features:

1. When you click on New Tab then you see New Images.
2. In Games section you see Latest Games, so just click on it and play Now.
3. Show & Hide Time .
4. Share With your friends.

Note:- This extension is only for Among Us Fans, When you add this extension you see your Chrome Wallpaper Was Changed.
